This paper is about formalizing the definition of Artificial Intelligence, which is a core topic in the field of AI. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.AI. The paper also discusses the level of intelligence of AI, which is related to machine learning and neural networks, making cs.LG and cs.NE likely sub-categories as well. The paper also introduces parameters for AI, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and robotics (cs.RO).
